  "detailed_description": "Relax in a serene temple garden, and enjoy a blissful game of simple strategy, based on the award-winning board game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/8845dcd7c45ba98dc801be0ca796e0fc.poster.avif?t=1601981631\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/8845dcd7c45ba98dc801be0ca796e0fc.webm?t=1601981631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/8845dcd7c45ba98dc801be0ca796e0fc.mp4?t=1601981631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create your own journey with <strong>Tsuro: The Game of the Path</strong>.<br><br>Place a tile and slide your stone along the path created, but take care: other players’ paths can lead you in the wrong direction - or off the board entirely!<br><br>Paths will cross and connect, and the choices you make affect all the journeys across the board.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/b631cd58834557d5dfece02d33524c71.poster.avif?t=1601981631\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/b631cd58834557d5dfece02d33524c71.webm?t=1601981631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/b631cd58834557d5dfece02d33524c71.mp4?t=1601981631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Relax in a serene temple garden, and enjoy a blissful game of simple strategy, based on the award-winning board game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/8845dcd7c45ba98dc801be0ca796e0fc.poster.avif?t=1601981631\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/8845dcd7c45ba98dc801be0ca796e0fc.webm?t=1601981631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/8845dcd7c45ba98dc801be0ca796e0fc.mp4?t=1601981631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create your own journey with <strong>Tsuro: The Game of the Path</strong>.<br><br>Place a tile and slide your stone along the path created, but take care: other players’ paths can lead you in the wrong direction - or off the board entirely!<br><br>Paths will cross and connect, and the choices you make affect all the journeys across the board.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/b631cd58834557d5dfece02d33524c71.poster.avif?t=1601981631\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/b631cd58834557d5dfece02d33524c71.webm?t=1601981631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111960/extras/b631cd58834557d5dfece02d33524c71.mp4?t=1601981631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
